{"tid":1240517,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[選民登記攻略] 2/7前截止，年底區議會戰場再開﹗制度內外，都要係香港人利益為依歸。","createTime":"2019-06-18T11:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T11:19:25.000Z","uid":113124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"540b753770c508203c26c52e0deb76921f4974f2","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:07:07.000Z","msg":"年底區議會再會進行選舉，大家必須於2/7前登記為選民﹗今天我以網上形式登記，並寫出方法如下，各位香港人，如果你想建制派成為過街老鼠，就要行動﹗<br />\n<br />\n登記流程主要有三個步驟﹕<br />\nA. 取得表格<br />\nB. 進行填寫<br />\nC. 遞交<br />\n<br />\nA. 取得表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C)_eSign.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Feform%2FREO-1%28C%29_eSign.pdf&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=a61e74c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/eform/REO-1(C)_eSign.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\nB. 進行填寫<br />\n1. 可於電腦直接填寫 (若PDF等軟件成功支援直接修改，很快便)<br />\n2. 可在手機上以Adobe Fill &amp; Sign進行修改 (較為難操作，可能我年紀大)<br />\n3. 可利用線上網頁PDF工具進行修改 <a href=\"https://smallpdf.com/zh-TW/edit-pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmallpdf.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fedit-pdf&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=59576143\" target=\"_blank\">https://smallpdf.com/zh-TW/edit-pdf</a><br />\n4. 可直接列印書寫<br />\n<br />\nC. 遞交<br />\n1. 線上遷交 <a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Fupload_form_reo1.jsp&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=feeb9a66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/upload_form_reo1.jsp</a> (但我上載不到)<br />\n2. 直接電郵 form@reo.gov.hk<br />\n3. 郵寄選舉事務處 (香港灣仔港灣道25號海港中心10樓)<br />\n4. 直接傳真 2891 1180<br />\n<br />\n網上亦有有心人寫好程式，直接填資料，直接下載成品(但是是2016年作品，不知可否用)﹗<br />\n<a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/app.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io%2Fapp.html&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=9ac6c3c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/app.html</a><br />\n<br />\n最後我選擇下載表格--&gt;網上修改--&gt;電郵處理<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/18/xj07d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F18%2Fxj07d6.png&h=96bbacd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE教學﹕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVCEjiY5EvY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRVCEjiY5EvY&d=qLBezvvtP0%2Ff8NIwCarvwg3x%2FUg%2Bgbtl8eFt0uNm3qw%3D&h=205c37a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RVCEjiY5EvY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢份文想寫得精簡，其實好快。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n其實我係一個好懶既人，但係呢一次，我真係要沉住氣好認真面對社會當前局勢。場面再艱難再辛苦，我地都要認真、冷靜、小心打落去。愈爛既牌愈要比心機打﹗香港人加油﹗"},{"pid":"9bbf8ef9d2182e8fe4c445d9fcc3a5a18cda15b7","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2016年 已登記選民380萬，投票者200萬。<br />\n如果大家萬眾一心，立法會將會風起雲湧!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"f69a70e1ce0c017b6eb4faaae8cbbe0455ae4e1e","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:11:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f511ee1c7558c41bbdf1537f5e38b0d28d01903","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e8a90e54c8a9d055dbf197c4e8ac2fe8a6f15b","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T11:12:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e2fbfa85f9b9223372af0e430e0bbd9d5003a8","tid":1240517,"uid":113124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:19:25.000Z","msg":"PUSSSSSSSSSSSH"}]}